{"type": "article", "id": 43693, "title": "家用废水怎么处理？有人做了个迷你雨林｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-02T22:56:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 42903, "name": "Paper Collective"}, {"id": 42904, "name": "MOEBE"}, {"id": 42905, "name": "DN Group"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 16057, "name": "Norm Architects"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 157, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170802180630xZG80OFybVRSQcBX.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Drop By Drop by Pratik Ghosh</h3><p>把“灰水”（除马桶排放的污水以外的家庭废水）收集起来浇花、冲洗马桶是相当常见的节水方法。除此之外，我们还有没有可能直接在家将它们净化、作为饮用水？针对这个问题，毕业于英国皇家艺术学院的 <a href=\"http://ki-kando.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pratik Ghosh</a> 设计了一个实用且美观的净化系统 Drop By Drop。Ghosh 的灵感来源于被称为地球之肺的亚马逊雨林，利用设置在玻璃罩上方的光源，促使内部的植物开始蒸腾作用，净化灰水。美中不足的是，Drop By Drop 目前最大的问题在于净化过程太过漫长：它需要 12 小时才能完成一次最多 160 升水的净化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017080218071906iQsy4HgB5pqhCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802180709LvfMam6guI7Ekt4S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802180719MZcNzDUCK9liutL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.301184\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802180720kPbzhW5TxtKuREAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lucky Clover Fruit Tray by Zelect</h3><p>以代表幸运的四叶草为灵感，<a href=\"https://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>旗下的设计师推出了一套温润简洁的白色果盘组。当高度不一的三款盘子组合在一起，又能营造出类似花瓣的层次感。果盘由耐碰的强化瓷制成，支持机洗。你可以通过<a href=\"https://zaozuo.com/item/300202\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为人民币 99 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181011GFXSj7Yp9N42MdPB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560185\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708021810116eUhN0tbTOFlYjVz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181012EkasS5cUhQ7eIK6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181011diaNZDl436UnrX7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Floating Leaves by Norm Architects et al.</h3><p>还记得那些夹在书里的植物书签吗，假如那些标本能够悬浮在空中又会是怎样的场景？最近，<a href=\"http://normcph.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Norm Architects</a>、经营艺术家合作款印刷品的 Paper Collective 与 <a href=\"http://www.moebe.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MOEBE</a> 这三个来自哥本哈根的丹麦设计公司联手推出了名为 Floating Leaves 的透明印刷品系列。摄影作品通过 UV 印刷工艺呈现在透明薄片上，让人产生一种这些植物凭空生长的错觉。从挂在花房中的效果图来看，真的可以以假乱真。你可以通过 Paper Collective 的<a href=\"https://paper-collective.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价为 17.95 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708021812276k0ZTX3eSzAOUmuD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181227bxswAf3EmyOXSMYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181227sPcUq6t9h0YDATwp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181227BLn5l8pMSi0ADCK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.401235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FODI</h3><p>除了产品及平面设计师之外，来自香港的 Kade Chan 还是一个专业的折纸艺术家，曾设计过 100 多个原创折纸产品。他的最新作品是一款与日本设计师 Kiho Satoshi 联手设计的多功能支架 <a href=\"http://www.fodi.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FODI</a>：平时它只是一张 1 毫米厚、重 40 克的“纸”，但只要沿着折痕折叠就能变化为两种不同的结构，撑起手机、平板设备和书都不在话下，最高 20 千克的承重意味着它甚至还能用作笔记本电脑支架。“纸”由聚丙烯（PP）和聚氯乙烯（PVC）制成，具有防水防污的特性。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fodi/fodi-the-flat-multi-purpose-origami-stand\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 14 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181253psCmuiSJ32NWQ8Xb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181254GMtQwHFXTmO8hyJ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708021812546Myv84saCnIEGeZh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181253p1bTcd9wHAntgRzK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181253AIjMlOszvEk0UBqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>To Camoe by DN Group</h3><p>俄罗斯设计工作室 <a href=\"http://d-n.group/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DN Group</a> 最近为冰淇淋品牌 To Camoe 设计了一套由几何风的包装，清淡的配色带给人一种甜而不腻的感觉。为了突出天然奶源以及与苏联时期相同的冰淇淋奶油含量标准，设计师特意参考了当时的广告海报设计，从中选取了比较具有代表性的图案，用来区别旗下的三款冰淇淋。两种蛋筒由实心和圆圈表示，三角形则代表雪糕。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181530SZVrgHoyenx0jdth.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181429S4mhKL2ts3p1ExUW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708021814295mBozcpKEkQGrVhD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708021814299yiIcZnD8qP2Opvr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Yokai series by Hanabiyori Tatami</h3><p>和朋友们围坐在一起、分享怪谈营造恐怖气氛是不少日本影视剧中出现的消暑方式，而在来自日本九州地区的插画师 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tatami111\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hanabiyori Tatami</a> 看来，妖怪们也可以走治愈系的路线。在 Tatami 笔下，寿司、清酒、盆栽甚至咖喱都变成了独一无二的妖怪们，有一部分“妖怪化”还源于物品本身与妖怪名之间的联系。以黄瓜寿司卷（kappamaki）为例，kappa 指的就是著名的河童妖。你还可以在 Tatami 的 <a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=7430269\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pixiv</a> 上看到更多作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181449O70HTjbZgIiSFtfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181449pqtr8CBwN4hQ9KIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181449haRQVe2yXtjspPf7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170802181450YyF97dUh3PJxceTb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}